<span id="freeTextContainer8216444106586563868">This short but suspenseful book by one of my favourite authors was a great quick read. I enjoyed the story and the characters of Natalie and Ryan. The mystery behind the fires and their investigation made me want to read on until I had finished the last page. I will always read books by this author because I just love her snappy style of suspense and romance mixed into these books which drag you quickly into each story.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


