<span id="freeTextContainer14476717846902352741">It&apos;s impossible for me to separate my nostalgia out of these rereads, but I swear, my brain clicks in satisfaction at the way these tightly written romances function so well. There&apos;s no excess plot, the conflicts never overstay their welcome, there&apos;s limited angst about feeling attraction to each other, even though that&apos;s the main conflict! What a blessing. I will continue to reread this book every 5-8 years in perfect contentment.</span>
